但因為未爆先封 反而經濟活動得以延續<br />\n歐美因一時利益賠上巨大既損失<br />\n如果今役都仲未認清中共假消息威力 咁以後真係叫歐豬美豬不為過<br />\nFool me once, shame on you<br />\nFool me twice, shame on me"},{"pid":"4ee9488e3bd4469075bc7b0181a2e0f55522a2c3","tid":1965120,"uid":136136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc85653c067233b29339dd4137852f0aa1114cb","tid":1965120,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"臺灣的未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857849e75a49794342b72f37fc91133c54c84c72","tid":1965120,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"香港都有許穎婷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62820f622f7212b07d7fd3654f6791463e85d91f","tid":1965120,"uid":124252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:00:01.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"53864d73846df1abb1dd8a2338ed1af9723d63cf","tid":1965120,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:00:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66a1913fa00757671002e848b339365d237546aa","tid":1965120,"uid":258109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83fc434f2951b5ebe73e84a330a5f2eaef023f5","tid":1965120,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6535fcb22dfc24aaf7a31f6615935b4804d0a415","tid":1965120,"uid":272422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:12:57.000Z","msg":"#StandWithTW<br />\n#TaiwanHelps <br />\n#DrTedros #WHO <br />\n#Coronavirus #COVID19"},{"pid":"c6bf8067cdab69d405