ircumstance. <br />\n<br />\n現在，我與我熱愛的國家和臺灣人民，要求您針對4/8的不實指控，提出道歉！<br />\n<br />\nThank you for your time.<br />\n感謝。<br />\n<br />\nVivi Lin<br />\n2020.4.8 <br />\n<br />\n#StandWithTW<br />\n#TaiwanHelps <br />\n#DrTedros #WHO <br />\n#Coronavirus #COVID19"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Stand with TW<br />\nStand with HK</span>"},{"pid":"bfafd6416eb611d02e210e896f04813d1939a49b","tid":1965120,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:30:58.000Z","msg":"奶共奶到盡"},{"pid":"3baf1952cb10144ce915ef6b4f77c2f292c28512","tid":1965120,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37aeebab90e5b994cd3d0fb4469deecdc0a3cd8c","tid":1965120,"uid":265192,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"23e676eb4e7abf8190154b14aaeaa2a8e1d6452b","tid":1965120,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:21:42.000Z","msg":"一句fuck you 力架咪得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"臺灣人：「臺灣是一個相信進步價值的國家，臺灣人民，更是始終尊重多元、擁抱多元」<br />\n<br />\n連登仔：「fuck you 力架」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />思想野蠻到同世界脫哂節仲學人講國際戰線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:31:50.000Z","msg":"因為好多台灣人屌柒佢黑人"},{"pid":"c4130c3fda5822dfea7cc4703bad9dc5610b125f","tid":1965120,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:32:21.000Z","msg":"CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb562feb50baaf495661adaf60b5835cea3edf8","tid":1965120,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f955176158e5958c3f7bba8cdac756df893aeea","tid":1965120,"uid":212944,"like":153,"dislike":3,"score":150,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:20:48.000Z","msg":"台灣人幫左我地咁多，希望大家都幫手推下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:34:13.000Z","msg":"香港人做抽水角色就可以"},{"pid":"8c05ca27caa8a1e74477